{"title":"用Pixel实现Scratch的移动xxx步","uid":"70b1f252b4587141a8c0385afcd95bb2","slug":"用Pixel实现Scratch的移动xxx步","date":"2024-02-14T06:51:20.000Z","updated":"2024-02-21T03:45:19.819Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/用Pixel实现Scratch的移动xxx步.json","keywords":"日常 编程","cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"需求\"><a href=\"#需求\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"需求\"></a>需求</h2><p>给Node添加一个void类型的成员函数Move，传入一个float类型实参step。调用此函数，节点可以向旋转方向移动step个像素的距离。</p>\n<h2 id=\"举例\"><a href=\"#举例\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"举例\"></a>举例</h2><p>当节点旋转0°、step为1时，x坐标增加1、y坐标增加0；当节点旋转45°、step为1时，x、y坐标各增加0.5；当节点旋转-135°、step为1时，x、y坐标各减少0.5……</p>\n<h2 id=\"分析\"><a href=\"#分析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"分析\"></a>分析</h2><p>从上面的例子可以发现：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>旋转角度在0°~90°内，x、y坐标各加上一个非负数。</li>\n<li>旋转角度在90°~180°内，x坐标减去一个非负数，y坐标加上一个非负数。</li>\n<li>旋转角度在180°~270°内，x、y坐标各减去一个非负数。</li>\n<li>旋转角度在270°~360°内，x坐标加上一个非负数，y坐标减去一个非负数。</li>\n<li>x、y坐标加上和减去的值的和等于1（不考虑step的值）。</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"实现\"><a href=\"#实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现\"></a>实现</h2><div class=\"language-cpp\"><button title=\"Copy code\" class=\"copy\"></button><span class=\"lang\">cpp</span><pre class=\"shiki github-dark\" style=\"background-color: #1a1a1a\" tabindex=\"0\"><code><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #F97583\">void</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B392F0\">Pixel</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">::</span><span style=\"color: #B392F0\">Node</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">::</span><span style=\"color: #B392F0\">Move</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">(</span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">float</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #FFAB70\">step</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">&#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">float</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> x </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">90</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">/</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> _angle, y </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">1</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">-</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> x;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">if</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">0</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> _angle </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">90</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        x </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        y </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">else</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">if</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">90</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> _angle </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">180</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        x </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">-</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        y </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">else</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">if</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">180</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> _angle </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">270</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        x </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">-</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        y </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">-</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">else</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">if</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> (</span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">270</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> _angle </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">&lt;=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #79B8FF\">360</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">)</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        x </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">        y </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">*=</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">-</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">step;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">else</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#123;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #6A737D\">        // 这里不需要考虑_angle&gt;360的情况，后续会在旋转的成员函数里做限制。</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    &#125;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">    </span><span style=\"color: #B392F0\">SetPosition</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">(</span><span style=\"color: #B392F0\">GetPosition</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">() </span><span style=\"color: #F97583\">+</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\"> </span><span style=\"color: #B392F0\">Vector2</span><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">(x, y));</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color: #E1E4E8\">&#125;</span></span></code></pre></div><h2 id=\"一点小小的吐槽\"><a href=\"#一点小小的吐槽\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一点小小的吐槽\"></a>一点小小的吐槽</h2><p>写这篇博文的原因是自己以后想把这个功能做进Pixel里，怕自己忘掉就记录了下来。<del>写的时候还因为记性不好翻了翻以前在纸上写的。</del></p>\n","text":"需求给Node